---
// Infra widget — "spec sheet" layout (uniform label/value lines, robust).
// Narrative: provisioning (GitOps) → access (edge) → services → resilience.
// Reality (01-Homelab repo): all guests on pve02; resilience = PBS + restic
// offsite + IaC replayable from git. NetBox dropped (OOS/decommission per planning).
---

<section id="infra">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head"><h2>Infrastructure</h2><div class="rule"></div></div>
    <p class="sec-intro">
      Le homelab qui sert de terrain à tout le reste — provisionné en code,
      exposé sans ouvrir un seul port à la maison, et conçu pour survivre
      à la perte de son nœud principal.
    </p>

    <div class="infra-panel">
      <div class="infra-bar">
        <span class="ib-title">homelab.topology</span>
        <span class="ib-iac">voir l'IaC → <em>bientôt</em></span>
      </div>

      <!-- build -->
      <div class="grp">
        <div class="line">
          <span class="k">provisioning</span>
          <span class="v">git push <i>→</i> Terraform + Ansible <i>→</i> Proxmox</span>
        </div>
        <div class="line">
          <span class="k">accès</span>
          <span class="v">internet <i>→</i> VPS Gateway <i>→</i> pve02 <span class="muted">· ~20 LXC en prod</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="line">
          <span class="k"></span>
          <span class="v muted">Caddy · Tailscale · Pocket ID · <b>0 port ouvert à la maison</b></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- services -->
      <div class="grp">
        <div class="line"><span class="k">edge &amp; sécurité</span><span class="v">Caddy · Tailscale · Pocket ID · AdGuard</span></div>
        <div class="line"><span class="k">observabilité</span><span class="v">Grafana · Prometheus · Loki · Uptime Kuma</span></div>
        <div class="line"><span class="k">apps</span><span class="v">Immich · Homepage · Paperless <span class="muted">· +12</span></span></div>
      </div>

      <!-- resilience -->
      <div class="grp resil">
        <div class="line">
          <span class="k"><span class="dot"></span>résilience</span>
          <span class="v"><b>PBS</b> local + <b>restic</b> offsite — 3-2-1 <em>restaurée-testée</em></span>
        </div>
        <div class="line">
          <span class="k"></span>
          <span class="v">infra <b>rejouable depuis Git</b> <span class="muted">— le nœud meurt, l'infra renaît</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #infra { padding: 64px 0; }

  .infra-panel {
    border: 2px solid var(--stone); border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--parchment);
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: var(--mono);
  }

  /* title bar */
  .infra-bar {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 11px 18px;
    background: var(--marble);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone);
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .ib-title { color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .ib-iac { color: var(--bronze); font-size: 11.5px; }
  .ib-iac em { font-style: normal; color: var(--ink-muted); opacity: .65; }

  /* groups separated by dividers */
  .grp { padding: 13px 18px; }
  .grp + .grp { border-top: 1px solid var(--stone); }

  /* uniform label / value line */
  .line { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: baseline; padding: 4px 0; }
  .line .k {
    flex: none; width: 124px;
    font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bronze-dark);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
  }
  .line .v { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.55; }
  .line .v i { font-style: normal; color: var(--bronze); padding: 0 3px; }
  .line .v b { color: var(--bronze-dark); font-weight: 600; }
  .line .v em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .line .v .muted { color: var(--ink-muted); }

  /* resilience band — highlighted */
  .resil {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(160,116,79,.08), rgba(160,116,79,.03));
    border-top: 2px solid var(--bronze-light) !important;
  }
  .resil .dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--bronze);
    flex: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .line { flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; padding: 6px 0; }
    .line .k { width: auto; }
  }
</style>
